snippet.title: SNES Classic Kong Complete
snippet.description:
how unfair that the mighty Super Nintendo never got a proper conversion of Nintendo's arcade classic "Donkey Kong". But have no fear, homebrew hero Bubblezap to the rescue! this is the second version of "Classic Kong" released to the public which now includes the pie factory level. you  can grab the free ROm and even the game's source code form his website.

Romhacking.net Game page: http://www.romhacking.net/homebrew/62/
